"de CrackLib avant de compiler Shadow. Puis ajoutez <parameter>--with-"
"libcrack</parameter> à la commande <command>configure</command> ci-dessous."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/shadow.xml:52
msgid ""
"Disable the installation of the <command>groups</command> program and its "
"man pages, as Coreutils provides a better version. Also, prevent the "
"installation of manual pages that were already installed in <xref linkend="
"\"ch-system-man-pages\"/>:"
msgstr ""
"Désactivez l'installation du programme <command>groups</command> et de ses "
"pages de manuel car Coreutils en fournit une meilleure version.  Cela "
"empêche aussi l'installation de pages de manuel déjà installées dans <xref "
"linkend=\"ch-system-man-pages\"/>&nbsp;:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/shadow.xml:57
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput remap=\"pre\">sed -i 's/groups$(EXEEXT) //' src/Makefile.in\n"
"find man -name Makefile.in -exec sed -i 's/groups\\.1 / /'   {} \\;\n"
"find man -name Makefile.in -exec sed -i 's/getspnam\\.3 / /' {} \\;\n"
"find man -name Makefile.in -exec sed -i 's/passwd\\.5 / /'   {} \\;</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput remap=\"pre\">sed -i 's/groups$(EXEEXT) //' src/Makefile.in\n"
"find man -name Makefile.in -exec sed -i 's/groups\\.1 / /'   {} \\;\n"
"find man -name Makefile.in -exec sed -i 's/getspnam\\.3 / /' {} \\;\n"
"find man -name Makefile.in -exec sed -i 's/passwd\\.5 / /'   {} \\;</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/shadow.xml:62
msgid ""
"Instead of using the default <emphasis>crypt</emphasis> method, use the more "
"secure <emphasis>SHA-512</emphasis> method of password encryption, which "
"also allows passwords longer than 8 characters. It is also necessary to "
"change the obsolete <filename class=\"directory\">/var/spool/mail</filename> "
"location for user mailboxes that Shadow uses by default to the <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/var/mail</filename> location used currently. And, get "
"rid of <filename class=\"directory\">/bin</filename> and <filename class="
"\"directory\">/sbin</filename> from <envar>PATH</envar>, since they are "
"simply symlinks to their counterpart in <filename class=\"directory\">/usr</"
"filename>."
msgstr ""
"Au lieu d'utiliser la méthode <emphasis>crypt</emphasis> par défaut, "
"utilisez la méthode <emphasis>SHA-512</emphasis> plus sécurisée du "
"chiffrement de mot de passe, qui autorise aussi les mots de passe plus longs "
"que huit caractères. Il est également nécessaire de changer l'emplacement "
"obsolète de <filename class=\"directory\">/var/spool/mail</filename> pour "
"les boîtes e-mail de l'utilisateur que Shadow utilise par défaut en "
"l'endroit <filename class=\"directory\">/var/mail</filename> utilisé "
"actuellement. Ensuite, retirez <filename class=\"directory\">/bin</filename> "
"et <filename class=\"directory\">/sbin</filename> de <envar>PATH</envar>, "
"car ce sont de simples liens symboliques vers leur contrepartie dans "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/usr</filename>."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><note><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/shadow.xml:75
msgid ""
"If <filename class=\"directory\">/bin</filename> and/or <filename class="
"\"directory\">/sbin</filename> are preferred to be left over in <envar>PATH</"
"envar> for some reason, modify <envar>PATH</envar> in <filename>.bashrc</"
"filename> after LFS is built."
msgstr ""
"Si vous préférez garder <filename class=\"directory\">/bin</filename> ou "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/sbin</filename> dans <envar>PATH</envar> pour "
"une raison ou une autre, modifiez <envar>PATH</envar> dans <filename>."
"bashrc</filename> après la construction de LFS."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/shadow.xml:82
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput remap=\"pre\">sed -e 's:#ENCRYPT_METHOD DES:ENCRYPT_METHOD SHA512:' \\\n"
"    -e 's:/var/spool/mail:/var/mail:'                 \\\n"
"    -e '/PATH=/{s@/sbin:@@;s@/bin:@@}'                \\\n"
"    -i etc/login.defs</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput remap=\"pre\">sed -e 's:#ENCRYPT_METHOD DES:ENCRYPT_METHOD SHA512:' \\\n"
"    -e 's:/var/spool/mail:/var/mail:'                 \\\n"
"    -e '/PATH=/{s@/sbin:@@;s@/bin:@@}'                \\\n"
"    -i etc/login.defs</userinput>"

